## IV. COMPLETE PYTHON IMPLEMENTATION

### Core Ξ-System Library

```python
"""
Ξ-SYSTEM: Complete Mathematical Framework
Author: Artit Pongpira
Date: 2026-07-09
License: OSL 3.0
